	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64590373"><p>This is explicitly taking away rubberstamping power from the executive branch and forcing them to argue their case in front of a separate branch of government(at the lower levels elected  and at the appeal level appointed) in which they can lose. By any rational measure, that is a net loss of power for the state.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64590373">

